name: SynthwavePunk
description:
This is a 50/50 Merge of Synthwave and InkPunk you can use both of their keywords and use prompt weighting to balance between these two cool and complimentary styles.

I'm on the search for V3! Check out these potential candidates and let me know which you prefer and if either of them are good enough to be the latest version of this model.

modelVersions.name: V2
modelVersions.description:
Upgraded to InkPunk V2.

This version definitely seems to have picked up more of the InkPunk side of things.

modelVersions.description:
I wanted something that gave characters a little more depth so I've been experimenting with merging in some other models. This one is the new JoMad model with SynthwavePunk V2 added as a difference.

Warning: The JoeMad model makes it nearly impossible to get things other than people...
